{
  "stem": "4764.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And very little food, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think the food-- the Poles used to throw the-- the chickens over the electric wires into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's how some people used to get some of their food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or some of their-- because-- and I remember also that the Red Cross used to send parcels.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And occasionally, a Red Cross parcel would arrive, and it had all sorts of goodies like I'd never seen before, like biscuits and chocolates and things.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that was-- but that was very rare.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember most of the time that my mother used to have a chicken and she used to burn it over the fire, sort of, to get rid of all the feathers before she could cook it.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I think that's how they got the food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not very much that I can remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing that-- that was-- that a child likes, anyway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing special that was-- that was something that I could remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I was always bribed with-- with chocolate to keep quiet if they had some.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I remember it must have been a very big treat to get a piece of chocolate, because I'd never had any of that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were other children there, but I don't remember playing with any of them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we were just-- I just had to sit in-- in-- inside and not even go outside.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my mother-- my parents were very worried about me going out on the street as just a small child.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I only went-- anywhere where I went, I went with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there's no memory of that at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't have a shower.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was-- it was sort of like a basin.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
